CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Lounging Model - Christine Sumpter, one of the D.I. models, lounges casually in beach attire on the "sands" of the Press Club during last Sunday's review."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Christine Sumpter wearing light colored bathing suit and shoes, standing in front of alternating light colored and dark curtains, two potted plants on metal stands on left, in home of Gloria Grate preparing for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue at the Press Club in the Hotel Sherwyn
